AHU Company Scraper

A scraper that collects company data from the AHU website (Indonesian business registry). It handles reCAPTCHA v3, rotates proxies, and includes detection-avoidance techniques.

In the test task, you mentioned two things that I did not implement.

The first was generating new keywords from the scraped company names to expand coverage. That part would be relatively easy to add.

However, there are two issues with the keyword search approach:

Example: searching "ind" shows ~200k results, but when navigating pages, around page 9 or 10 it starts showing "not found".
If the goal is to collect all companies from the AHU website, the keyword approach alone may not guarantee full coverage.

Current Status
Collected so far: 650+ companies
Keywords searched: 62
Keyword set generated: All 3-letter combinations (aaa → zzz, total 17,576)

This keyword set should theoretically cover ~170k unique companies.

The scraper can run much faster if we:

Use 100 proxies
Increase concurrency to 30 workers

With that setup, it should be possible to collect ~10k unique companies in about 10 minutes.

Why didn’t I reach 10k?

I ran out of 2Captcha credits. With sufficient credits, collecting 10k companies in ~20 minutes should be achievable.

Main Problems
✅ Problem 1: Geo-blocking & reCAPTCHA (Solved)

The AHU website blocks foreign IPs and triggers reCAPTCHA.

Solution implemented:

Use Indonesian proxy IPs
Solve reCAPTCHA using 2Captcha

❌ Problem 2: Pagination (Not solved yet)

Example issue:

Search "ind" → shows ~200k results
But when navigating pages, around page 9–10 the site returns "not found"

If this pagination issue can be solved, it should be possible to scrape all 2+ million companies on AHU.

The main question is:
Why does AHU stop returning results early even though more results exist?

Keyword Generation

The scraper generates all 17,576 three-letter combinations (aaa → zzz).

AHU requires a minimum of 3 characters, so this approach helps cover a wide range of company names.

Features:

Resumable: The scraper can stop anytime and continue from where it left off.
Restart: Delete companies.csv to start from scratch.
No duplicates: Company NBR IDs are tracked across all workers.


Project Structure (Simple)
ahu_scraper/
├── main.py                 # Run this
├── config/
│   ├── setting.py          # All settings
│   ├── proxies.txt         # Indonesian proxies
│   └── completed_keywords.json  # Tracks completed keywords
├── scraper/
│   ├── worker.py           # Main scraping logic
│   ├── helper.py           # Proxy & CSV utilities
│   ├── page_parser.py      # Extracts company data
│   └── captcha_solver.py   # 2Captcha integration
├── database/
│   ├── companies.csv       # Scraped companies
│   └── keywords.csv        # All 17,576 keywords
└── logs/
    └── scraper.log         # Logs


Setup
python3.11 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m patchright install chromium --with-deps


Set your 2Captcha API key in .env:

echo "2CAPTCHA_API_KEY=your_key" > .env

Run
python main.py


Note:
Proxies and configuration are already set up for direct testing.